                  <h3>Convert any video file to <b style="color:black;background-color:#a0ffff">DVD</b> with open source tools</h3>
                 <div class="xar-article-details">
                            By <a href="mailto:manolis AT tzanidakis DOT gr">Manolis Tzanidakis</a>
on
April 27, 2006 (8:00:00 AM)</div>
        <p style="text-align: right">
<!-- ADDTHIS BUTTON BEGIN -->
<script type="text/javascript">
